videos.headline: Francois puts FSU on the board with 8-yd TD
videos.description: Deondre Francois connects with Jacques Patrick for an 8-yard Seminole touchdown.

videos.headline: Akers runs untouched for 7-yard TD
videos.description: Cam Akers strolls into the end zone for a 7-yard Florida State touchdown.

videos.headline: NIU scores its first points of the game on 20-yard TD pass
videos.description: Marcus Childers finds Jauan Wesley for a 20-yard Huskies touchdown.

videos.headline: Childers, Brown link up on 66-yard NIU TD
videos.description: Marcus Childers finds an opening and throws deep to D.J. Brown, who runs into the end zone for a 66-yard Northern Illinois touchdown.

videos.headline: FSU continues to cruise as Francois makes incredible 78-yard TD pass
videos.description: Deondre Francois goes deep and connects with Tamorrion Terry for a 78-yard Florida State touchdown.

videos.headline: Childers closes the gap with 11-yard TD run
videos.description: NIU's Marcus Childers weaves through the Florida State defense for an 11-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Rasul seals the deal with 7-yard TD run
videos.description: Florida State's Amir Rasul squeezes into the end zone for a 7-yard touchdown.
